{"tid":133611,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲食過尚鮮日式燒肉漁市場?","createTime":"2017-02-24T17:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T08:55:11.000Z","uid":77381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"370bf99c0263ab55fb1a232a286646ada6f88e54","tid":133611,"uid":77381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"見間野有好多好評 好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又好似好多廣告咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想問下有無巴絲食過 覺得點呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都成三舊水位 驚中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6403fd2fa476c3b2c2b38d397ec0b101933b6cd","tid":133611,"uid":78865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"10分滿分有6-7分<br />\n<br />\n不過$300我寧願食炑八"},{"pid":"3195f91f3381b47b42cda34c61a1d58249295ce7","tid":133611,"uid":77381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10分滿分有6-7分<br />\n<br />\n不過$300我寧願食炑八</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無食果個咩甲羅燒?好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想日式燒肉 巴打又有無其他推介?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66658398c25b17ef4393744b5bb0377e1837acd9","tid":133611,"uid":77381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e28c82367d650fe40f03a22d9d2e2bc7c6a40d1","tid":133611,"uid":1275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食物質素係唔差嘅 係個爐細咗啲咁啦<br />\n坐就好鬆動下"},{"pid":"4a29e40b233c8481f786dcaa3b3aa0b9c7411a97","tid":133611,"uid":77381,"like":0,"dislik